txt.en: Dangerous crocodiles infest Ilmabiri, the sewers beneath the Sail-haven of Umbar Baharbêl. You should reduce their numbers.
You have reduced the number of crocodiles in the sewers. You should tell Ahûd at the guard post in the northern part of the Ilmabiri.
Dangerous crocodiles infest Ilmabiri, the sewers beneath the Sail-haven of Umbar Baharbêl.
Reducing the number of crocodiles in Ilmabiri should help prevent more incidents of them causing havoc in the Sail-haven.
'You are very bold, [placeholder]! Thank you for culling the crocodiles. That should help us indeed!'
